org.digijava.module.budgetexport.action

Class BudgetExportMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.budgetexport.action.BudgetExportMapper

  • public class BudgetExportMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    helper and container class which implements rewriting accesses to v_donor_funding metadata columns to corresponding columns in different column views.
    this is needed for BudgetExport reports which have hierarchies on fields which are contained in funding metadata
